n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0232f6c008668d8946e215160604e598fff21194","tid":246151,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:05:45.000Z","msg":"Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23fd2b090d6b0934f2f0f3b240a728322174181e","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2aedd08f914fe59d22f1e5d536ab0944628777c","tid":246151,"uid":7430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:10:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔撚記得lu~~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想問咩不過<br />\n連登有好多籮友 可能答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95659802f1e19ccc84f113d56918412bfd6d69d3","tid":246151,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:13:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45f432f743d3bde2aa2f3a573c744ea9ab4078bb","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我有病，個病令我訓教呼吸唔好，於是經醫生專介我買左部睡眠呼吸機。<br />\n用左一個月發覺部野開開下會隨機熄機，所以我知道呢件事亦都拎左去整。<br />\n有一次返工渣車，無啦啦渣渣下無左意識，撞左落 B 架車度，B 整親手。<br />\n醫生診斷我係因為前一晚呼吸唔好，引致當日失去意識，於是我之後拎返部睡眠呼吸機比廠商檢查，原來前一晚真係自動熄左機。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪只可以經 contract law sue 間廠商，而呢間廠商無 duty of care (proximity) to me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢件事 B 知道我都無心，所以無 sue 我拎 compensation。<br />\n點知幾年後，B 去滑雪手臂失去控制，然後跌傷，睇醫生發現 B 手臂有舊患，再睇返原來之前個醫生份 X-ray 都睇到 B 手臂有傷，不過一時唔留意所以無講比 B 知，再引發呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n咁 B 係咪可以經 tort law sue 個 醫生 &amp; 我有 breach of duty 引致佢有 causation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁可以追溯既日期就由佢發現自己有手傷個日計起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d323c4f07f6d416a48e5212200fd4d0b5656978","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:20:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔撚記得lu~~~~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你想問咩不過<br />\n連登有好多籮友 可能答到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常感謝"},{"pid":"35e0cf8a1c89d397e00e