citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:27:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"987f099dddc6cf72120017b81215219f0f819e8c","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:27:58.000Z","msg":"背緊 legal method &amp; sources of English law <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d592afe2a4f08a00af728f231062496c38a5aefa","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:28:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Gauss Law, Kirchhoff Law 我都輕鬆搞得掂，但 contract law tort law 真係好難搞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鏗哥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9a69350d821ba637302db94245a687c8b53b678","tid":246151,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我有病，個病令我訓教呼吸唔好，於是經醫生專介我買左部睡眠呼吸機。<br />\n用左一個月發覺部野開開下會隨機熄機，所以我知道呢件事亦都拎左去整。<br />\n有一次返工渣車，無啦啦渣渣下無左意識，撞左落 B 架車度，B 整親手。<br />\n醫生診斷我係因為前一晚呼吸唔好，引致當日失去意識，於是我之後拎返部睡眠呼吸機比廠商檢查，原來前一晚真係自動熄左機。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪只可以經 contract law sue 間廠商，而呢間廠商無 duty of care (proximity) to me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢件事 B 知道我都無心，所以無 sue 我拎 compensation。<br />\n點知幾年後，B 去滑雪手臂失去控制，然後跌傷，睇醫生發現 B 手臂有舊患，再睇返原來之前個醫生份 X-ray 都睇到 B 手臂有傷，不過一時唔留意所以無講比 B 知，再引發呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n咁 B 係咪可以經 tort law sue 個 醫生 &amp; 我有 breach of duty 引致佢有 causation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁可以追溯既日期就由佢發現自己有手傷個日計起 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n* 當時 B 個醫生只係話比 B 知係普通擦傷，無發現到手臂內部有絲裂</blockquote><br />\n係咪應該 sue 埋間醫院，個 Prof 教我地 sue 最有 $ 果個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4253487cc8da33b90d0b231aaf3e4e634ce4986","tid":246151,"uid":37874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T20:30:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Caparo test 係基本<br />\n點會唔考啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n絲打，想問你個 case <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我有病，個病令我訓教呼吸唔好，於是經醫生專介我買左部睡眠呼吸機。<br />\n用左一個月發覺部野開開下會隨機熄機，所以我知道呢件事亦都拎左去整。<br />\n有一次返工渣車，無啦啦渣渣下無左意識，撞左落 B 架車度，B 整親手。<br />\n醫生診斷我係因為前一晚呼吸唔好，引致當日失去意識，於是我之後拎返部睡眠呼吸機比廠商檢查，原來前一晚真係自動熄左機。<br />\n<br />\n我係咪只可以經 contract law sue 間廠商，而呢間廠商無 duty of care (proximity) to me <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢件事 B 知道我都無心，所以無 sue 我拎 compensation。<br />\n點知幾年後，B 去滑雪手臂失去控制，然後跌傷，睇醫生發現 B 手臂有舊患，再睇返原來之前個醫生份 X-ray 都睇到 B 手臂有傷，不過一時唔留意所以無講比 B 知，再引發呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n咁 B 係咪可以經 t